## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for education.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers learning visibility,
evaluation state,
completion state,
historical education reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- education context must resolve
- participation/evaluation basis must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid education context
- invalid evaluation basis
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish learning state,
evaluation state,
completion state,
historical reference,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- education runtime scope is explicit
- evaluation-aware rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
